link: G. C. Greubel, Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..950
Index entries for linear recurrences with constant coefficients, signature (8,40,-60,-40,8,1).
formula: a(n) = L(5*n) + 5*(-1)^n*L(3*n) + 10*L(n), L(n) = A000032, the Lucas numbers.
